==Russian==
[[Category:Russian adjectives]]
===Etymology===
Adjective made from Russian noun [[боец]] (fighter, warrior), from [[бой]] (battle, fight, combat).

===Adjective===
'''бойцовый''', бойцовая, бойцовое, бойцовые (bojtsóvyj, bojtsóvaja, bojtsóvoje, bojtsóvyje) ''m/f/n/pl''

# having a solid, muscular build ''(said of [[fighting cock]]s, [[gamecock]]s)''

